<item>
            <title>[SOLR-17057] JSON Query regression; defType doesn&apos;t work in &quot;params&quot;</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-17057</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The following test fails (&quot;undefined field all&quot;) but used to work prior to &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-16916&quot; title=&quot;JSON Query DSL doesn&amp;#39;t work if defType isn&amp;#39;t lucene&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-16916&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-16916&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
    client.testJQ(
        params(
            &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;json&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;{\n&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
                + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;    &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;query&apos;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;+all:NY&apos;&lt;/span&gt;,\n&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
                + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;    &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;fields&apos;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;*&apos;&lt;/span&gt;,\n&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
                + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;    &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;offset&apos;&lt;/span&gt;: 0,\n&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
                + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;    &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;limit&apos;&lt;/span&gt;: 10,\n&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
                + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;    &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;params&apos;&lt;/span&gt;: {\n&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
                + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;defType&apos;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;edismax&apos;&lt;/span&gt;,\n&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
                + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;f.all.qf&apos;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;id cat_s where_s&apos;&lt;/span&gt;\n&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
                + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;   }\n&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
                + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;}&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
        ),
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;response/numFound==2&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
    );
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
